  "prompt": "Do employees at Select Income REIT have a good work-life balance? Does this differ across positions and departments?",
  "response": "As of my last update in October 2023, specific information about employee satisfaction regarding work-life balance at Select Income REIT or in-depth reviews segmented by position and department is not readily available. Generally, work-life balance can vary significantly across different companies, departments, and individual positions within a firm.\n\nTo gather insights about work-life balance at Select Income REIT, I recommend looking at employee reviews on job review websites such as Glassdoor or Indeed. Additionally, you might consider checking the company's career page or reaching out to current or former employees via professional networking platforms like LinkedIn to get a clearer picture of the work environment.\n\nFactors that typically influence work-life balance in a company include organizational culture, management practices, workload, flexibility in work hours, and remote work options, all of which may vary between departments and roles within the firm.",
